The '''End highlands''' is a biome used to generate the [[Terrain features#Outer island|outer End island]]s.

== Description ==
This biome generates as part of the outer islands of [[the End]], forming the hill-tops in the center of each island. This is the only biome where [[chorus tree]]s naturally generate. [[End cities]] also generate here.
